This paper is likely to belong to the Multimedia (cs.MM) category as it deals with hiding data within a video file. It could also belong to the Cryptography and Security (cs.CR) category as it discusses the security issues related to data hiding. Computer Vision (cs.CV) is another possible category as the paper deals with image processing techniques. Information Theory (cs.IT) is also a likely category as the paper discusses the theory behind Bit Plane Complexity Segmentation. Finally, Machine Learning (cs.LG) could be a possible category as the paper proposes a collaborative approach for selecting frames, which could involve machine learning techniques.
